name: Jordan Retro 11 (XI) "Gamma" Men's Now Shipping!!!!
description:
This holiday seasons most anticipated release is here, The Air Jordan 11 “Gamma Blue” has been on everyone’s wish list since they were officially announced to release.  The Air Jordan 11 has always been a big deal to sneakerheads around Christmas time. Usually Jordan Brand release a retro of the Air Jordan 11 silhouette, but this time we have a never before seen version of the sneaker.
The new colorway features a predominantly Black upper with accents of Gamma Blue and Yellow which leads people to believe it might be a “Laney” inspired colorway.  A Blue tinted translucent sole finishes off the sneaker look adding to the subtle design.  Set to release December 21st, I’m sure we’re all hoping for an early Christmas.

Now Shipping 100% Authentic

name: Jordan Retro 12 "Taxi" Men's Shipping Now!!!
description:
Holiday 2013 boasts an extremely attractive roster of retro heat, and perhaps no shoe is more anticipated (perhaps) than the Air Jordan 12 Taxi, release date for which is set for December 14.

Remaining impressively faithful to the original, the shoe’s “rising sun”-stitched upper dons white tumbled leather, set against starkly contrasting reptile-embossed black leather at the forefoot. Gold metal eyelets appear on the collar and, finally, a yellow heel-tab inspires the shoe’s “Taxi” moniker.

name: Jordan Retro 11 (XI) Retro – Space Jams (Black / Varsity Royal – White)
description: The Air Jordan 11 (XI) Retro – Space Jams (Black / Varsity Royal – White) may be the most adored of the Air Jordan 11 (XI). They are dubbed the Space Jams because they were worn by MJ in the 1996 movie. They feature a black upper, which includes black patent leather, along with a varsity royal Jumpman logo. The white midsole, which does stand out and draw attention to the shoe, sits on a clear outsole, which looks yellow here because they tend to turn that way with use and even by simply sitting there, as the oxygen in the air will do that to them. The Air Jordan 11 (XI) draws inspiration from a tuxedo design, and it is quite evident with the patent leather, and many of the colorways.

Equally interesting is the premium packaging, which spells out the intent of the Elements line with some cool inserted materials.

name: Supreme x Northface fur print vest
description:
This Winter, New York street wear brand, Supreme, has yet again joined with leaders in winter wear, The North Face to introduce their new fur print Nuptse Jacket and fur print Nuptse Vest. This gives the term “faux fur” an entirely new meaning. PETA would be proud. Exclusively made for Supreme, The Nuptse Jacket and Nuptse Vest will both feature a water resistant nylon shell with 700 goose down fill. Double layer abrasion resistant taffeta on shoulders and taffeta emergency hood with reflective Supreme logo print. 

Brand new still in the bag bought from supreme LA on the release date.

name: ASICS X HIGHS AND LOWS " MORTAR"
description:
*Brand: Asics

*Condition: Brand New

*This sale is for the "Mortar" Gel Lyte III Only!!! This is not a pack!!!
 Grey Gel Lyte III only!!!

Australian sneaker retailer Highs and Lows has hooked up with ASICS this season to produce the “Brick and Mortar” pack — a reference to the “metaphorical mud and clay that keeps Highs and Lows together.” The two-shoe pack consists of the GT II and the Gel Lyte III. The “Brick” GT II features a rich red nubuck upper with subtle white accents and a white sole. The “Mortar” Gel Lyte III features a clean grey nubuck upper with a perforated toe box and midfoot panels. Subtle red and white accents tie the design together.
